high_descs: go forward a few steps and turn to the right and go to the sink
pick up the knife from the sink
turn to the right twice and take a few steps and  turn to the left and  go to the door and turn to the left facing the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and slice with the knife the tomato on the shelf and close the door
turn to the left and go to the front of the sink and turn to the right facing the sink
put the knife in the sink
turn to the right and go to the door and turn to the left facing the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and pick up a slice of tomato from the shelf and close the refrigerator door
turn to the left twice and take a few steps and turn to the right and go to the microwave
put the tomato slice in the microwave and cook and take out the cooked tomato slice
turn to the right twice and go to the front of the refrigerator and turn to the left and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and put the slice of tomato on the shelf and close the refrigerator door
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato slice in the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn right and head to the fridge.
Cut the tomato in the fridge.
Turn left and go back to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn right and go back to the fridge.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the fridge.
Turn left and head to the microwave above the stove.
Cook the slice of tomato in the microwave and pick the slice of tomato back up.
Turn around and go back to the fridge.
Put the slice of tomato in the fridge on the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the sink
Pick up the butter knife from the sink
Go to the fridge
Open the fridge, cut the tomato with the knife, and close the fridge
Go back to the sink
Put the knife down in the sink
Go back to the fridge
Open the fridge, pick a tomato slice up from the fridge, and close the fridge
Turn to your left and go to the stove
Put the tomato slice in the microwave above the stove, warm it for 7 seconds, take it out, and close the microwave
Take the tomato slice and go back to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the slice on the tray with the tomato, and close the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato in the fridge
